div.p:
24. Ground Force. The Communist ground forces in
                            Korea are capable of the following courses of action: 
                                a.

A large-scale offensive with little or no warning;
                                b.

Offensives to obtain limited objectives;
                                c.

Defense in depth for a prolonged period of time;
                                d.

Defense on successive positions;
                                e.

Limited guerrilla operations in South Korea.
